name: histone-lysine N-methyltransferase
reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + histone L-lysine = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + histone N6-methyl-L-lysine [RN:R03938]
comment: One of a group of enzymes methylating proteins; see also EC 2.1.1.59, [cytochrome-c]-lysine N-methyltransferase and EC 2.1.1.60, calmodulin-lysine N-methyltransferase.
